        <heading>4908.  New trial; procedure in parish or city courts</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4908.  New trial; procedure in parish or city courts
The application for new trial, and the new trial, when granted, shall be governed by the provisions of Article 1971 and Articles 1975 through 1979.</p>
        </content>
